{"type": "article", "id": 17464, "title": "一种叫“糙”的病迷之流行，你还有救吗？", "description": "一块肥皂可以洗脸洗手洗衣服洗全部……", "date": "2015-11-13T06:43:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 11405, "name": "好奇心研究所"}], "category": 5, "author": 112725, "comment_count": 16, "praise_count": 133, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702112922k8hMCLspofIa43ij.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t好奇心研究所的微博（<span>@</span>好奇心研究所）和微信公众号（<span>ID</span>：<span>QLab42</span>）全面上线啦，关注就可以与所长亲密接触。<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t“糙”，是一种由于懒癌引发的病体特征。主要临床表现为：对护肤品的极度不了解；对发型<span>/</span>食物<span>/</span>穿搭几乎零要求；能简则简，能不动弹则不动弹；在与他人的精致生活对比时容易受到强烈的心理刺激倍感羞愧。<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t糙也分深浅，过分的糙则变异成邋遢，轻度的糙则有一种随意的萌感，简称“糙萌”。为了对广大所员进行深入的治疗，本报「好奇心研究所」做过一次“你什么时候会觉得自己活得“糙”？”的投票，我们收获了共 9614 次表态。以下是一些病症：\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<strong>1. 不出门坚决不洗头，实在要出门又不想洗头就戴帽子，刘海太脏就只洗刘海。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702112910snbXkzhE0qFW6yio.gif\" width=\"500\" height=\"200\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.4\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<strong>2. 为什么要用护发素？（</strong><span><strong>@ rainbow</strong></span><strong>小姐的美好生活）</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702112911ziRT9VtdrNf5lPhq.gif\" width=\"500\" height=\"214\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.428\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<strong>3. 马尾every day，出门梳头基本靠手抓（</strong><span><strong>@ </strong></span><strong>晨光要起床）</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702112912RHmBuMysFpJxQknb.gif\" width=\"260\" height=\"173\" title=\"3\" alt=\"3\" data-ratio=\"0.66538462\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<strong>4. 头发是自己剪的。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702112913cbO3iIluEjH6V15e.gif\" width=\"500\" height=\"323\" title=\"3\" alt=\"3\" data-ratio=\"0.646\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<strong>5. 脸裸奔（</strong><span><strong>@ pink</strong></span><strong>）</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702112913kSngMi1dJFu3CKGb.gif\" width=\"900\" height=\"506\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.56222222\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<strong>6. 没有镜子</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<strong>二十年来只用清水洗脸</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<strong>防晒霜</strong><span><strong>/</strong></span><strong>隔离霜</strong><span><strong>/</strong></span><strong>乳液</strong><span><strong>/</strong></span><strong>眼霜是什么东西？</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702112914k5ENdCWtzDVHOXge.gif\" width=\"1080\" height=\"608\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.56296296\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<strong>7. 总共就一只别人送的唇膏，还不知道放哪儿了。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702112915wUYC20HeaPEpfcWM.gif\" width=\"500\" height=\"281\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.562\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<strong>8. 身边的男同事告诉我，他一周修两次眉（</strong><span><strong>@ </strong></span><strong>方方银）</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702112916i0k9MQGbBtl8ZIzc.gif\" width=\"500\" height=\"264\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.528\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<strong>9. 啥？你们内衣都成套穿吗？”（</strong><span><strong>@ mmmg</strong></span><strong>）</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702112916kpzOse1Pjd64IUbm.gif\" width=\"658\" height=\"394\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.59878419\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<strong>10. 春夏秋冬不管穿什么衣服都只背同一个包。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016070211291790QkdL81D5vCNAgF.gif\" width=\"500\" height=\"168\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.336\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<strong>11. 洗澡只要一首歌的时间（</strong><span><strong>@ </strong></span><strong>羊排）</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021129189wG2JBY4NERWV7xh.gif\" width=\"360\" height=\"203\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.56388889\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<strong>12. 吃水果皮都懒得削，直到有一天看见隔壁室友吃水果会切块摆盘。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702112918SMvDyt8G2ihcld9H.gif\" width=\"400\" height=\"225\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<strong>13. 别人吃牛排，我吃辣条（</strong><span><strong>@ </strong></span><strong>歪歪）</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702112919VOm4azo8WAurQGJb.gif\" width=\"400\" height=\"280\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.7\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<strong>14. 牛奶才过期五天，喝了又不会死。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702112920YKLJCWfM8G7TQepO.gif\" width=\"500\" height=\"275\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.55\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<strong>15. 一堆穿过的袜子里，挑不出还能穿的了。</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702112921AIMsLowO5zU8nXaF.gif\" width=\"500\" height=\"277\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.554\" data-format=\"gif\"></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<strong>16. 买个甜筒，要了番茄酱，放一起当圣代吃。</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/201607021129217KQ6lzV2NnRYJqZB.gif\" width=\"700\" height=\"385\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.55\" data-format=\"gif\"></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<span><i><a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/labs.html\">好奇心研究所</a></i></span><em>是好奇心日报的一个调查栏目，这是一个探讨各种生活方式问题的互动平台，它针对的可能是生活方式的变化和潮流，也可能是某个品牌的服务。你可以在这里投票、吐槽、表明态度。</em> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}